name: Greta Thunberg
text:
We're today discussing a #WorldWithoutNature as if it meant that "our children won't be able to see pandas in the future" or that "we won't be able to eat certain types of food".
A world without nature is no world. Stop separating "humans" and "nature". Humans are part of nature.
